   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="header">
            <p>Verwandtschafts weisung für Kaspar, Wolfgang, Esther und Martha, Kinder des Stephan
               Frawn- dor.fJer</p>
         </div>                   <div type="entry" resp="rs">
            <p>
               <rs type="event" ref="#ev__StB_I_7">Einbr. 2 Zg. (Indez: Item frewntsehaft Stepfans
                  Frawndorffer) Des nachsten sambcztags vor sand Niclas tag kom auch fur den rat <rs
                     type="fn" role="witness"><rs type="person"
                        ref="#pe__stephan_frauendorfer_ii_QGW_II_I_1339">Stephan der
                        Frawndorffer</rs> und hat da beweist mit den zwayn <rs type="person"
                        ref="#pe__pilgrim_snaeczl_QGW_II_I_1015"><roleName type="title">erbern
                        </roleName> mannen Piligreymen dem Sneczlein </rs> und mit <rs type="person"
                        ref="#pe__erasmus_malczer_QGW_II_I_1201">
                        <roleName type="title"><add>erbern</add></roleName>Erasem dem <roleName
                           type="prof" cert="unknown">Mallezer</roleName></rs></rs> , das <rs
                     type="fn" role="recipient">seinew vyr <rs type="person"
                        ref="#pe__kaspar_QGW_II_I_1347"><roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__stephan_frauendorfer_ii_QGW_II_I_1339">chinder</roleName>
                        Caspar</rs>, <rs type="person" ref="#pe__wolfgang_QGW_II_I_1347"><roleName
                           type="kin" corresp="#pe__stephan_frauendorfer_ii_QGW_II_I_1339"
                              ><add>chinder</add></roleName>Wolfgang</rs>, <rs type="person"
                        ref="#pe__esther_QGW_II_I_1347"><roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__stephan_frauendorfer_ii_QGW_II_I_1339"
                           ><add>chinder</add></roleName>Ester</rs> und <rs type="person"
                        ref="#pe__martha_QGW_II_I_1347"><roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__stephan_frauendorfer_ii_QGW_II_I_1339"
                           ><add>chinder</add></roleName>Martha</rs></rs> mit <rs type="fn"
                     role="issuer"><rs type="person" ref="#pe__jakob_chetner_QGW_II_I_1104">Jacoben
                        dem <roleName type="prof" cert="unknown">Chetner</roleName>, <rs
                           type="person" ref="#pe__konrad_chetner_QGW_II_I_1339"><roleName
                              type="dead"><add>got genad</add></roleName>Chunrats sun des
                           Chettner</rs>, den bayden <roleName type="dead">got gnad</roleName>,
                           <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__kaspar_QGW_II_I_1347">geswystreyd
                           enynkchel</roleName><roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__wolfgang_QGW_II_I_1347"><add>geswystreyd
                           enynkchel</add></roleName><roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__esther_QGW_II_I_1347"><add>geswystreyd
                           enynkchel</add></roleName><roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__martha_QGW_II_I_1347"><add>geswystreyd
                           enynkchel</add></roleName></rs> gewesen sind. </rs>Als darumb die
                  obgenanten erbern leut mit irn trewn an ayde stat vor offem rat habent gesagt, als
                  si ze recht solten.</rs>
            </p>
         </div>
